item.title: ICURFC 3rd XV win uphill against St Georges
item.author: Lukas Michalitsch,
item.description: After a chequered first term for Imperial College 3rd XV and a great performance resulting in a disappointing draw against King’s Medics three weeks ago the social side of ICURFC wanted to show what they are capable of and bring home the first win this term.
